OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,FAn eyewitness has described the
OL,7,Fintensity of the huge fire which took
OL,8,Fhold at the TATA Steel site overnight.
OL,10,FBarry Evans arrived at the scene
OL,11,Fshorty after the fire began to spread,
OL,13,F"It was really concerning and
OL,14,Fworrying... It was such a challenging
OL,15,Fevening with the high winds.
OL,17,F"It was terrible, it was moving so
OL,18,Fquickly."
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
