OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F451A1781394468
OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,FBarry, who is chairman of the Port
OL,7,FTalbot site for Community union,
OL,8,Fpraised the work of emergency services
OL,9,Ffor safely evacuating people on site,
OL,11,F"It was really worrying times. It was
OL,12,Fa fantastic job by everyone on site,
OL,13,Fthe workers and management.
OL,15,F"The emergency services were
OL,16,Ftremendous by making sure everyone
OL,17,Fevacuated safely."
