OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F451A1781394468
OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,FMid and West Wales Fire service
OL,7,Fconfirmed that they were called to the
OL,8,Fincident at 8:06pm on Wednesday, June
OL,9,F3, with crews from 16 local stations
OL,10,Fattending to the blaze.
OL,12,FResidents from a mile away said they
OL,13,Fcould hear alarms sounding and could
OL,14,Fsmell the smoke.
OL,16,FBarry said the damage has been
OL,17,Fsignificant:
OL,19,F"There is a lot of damage
OL,20,Funfortunately. The winds made things
OL,21,Fmuch worse.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
