OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F451A1781394468
OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,F"It was moving so quickly... It was
OL,7,Freally challenging to see how quickly
OL,8,Fthe fire was spreading."
OL,10,FIt's another setback for the local
OL,11,Fcommunity, but Barry said they remain
OL,12,Fresilient:
OL,14,F"It's another kick in the teeth. But
OL,15,Fthe benefit here is that we (have) got
OL,16,Fsuch a resilient workforce. The
OL,17,Fworkers will step up to the challenge
OL,18,Fand we will come over this stronger."
OL,26,@pD@XO]wD@]pmwD@bpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
