OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,FTATA steel have confirmed all
OL,7,Fpersonnel have been accounted for and
OL,8,Fevacuated.
OL,10,FIn a statement released at 8am this
OL,11,Fmorning TATA said: "Mid and West Wales
OL,12,FFire Service attended the Port Talbot
OL,13,Fsite last night at around 8pm to deal
OL,14,Fwith a fire at one of the site's
OL,15,Fprocessing lines. All personnel were
OL,16,Faccounted for and evacuated from the
OL,17,Farea safely.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
