FL,452,430,260,120,000,100
PN,45106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F451A1781394468
OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,F"At this time, the emergency services
OL,7,Fremain on site and are working with
OL,8,Flocal teams to completely extinguish
OL,9,Fthe fire.
OL,11,F"The incident is not related to the
OL,12,Fsafe and successful demolition of the
OL,13,Fempty, redundant Gas Holder earlier
OL,14,Fyesterday evening.
OL,16,F"We would like to thank local site
OL,17,Fteams and the emergency services for
OL,18,Ftheir prompt and professional action."
OL,20,F"Further updates will be shared as
OL,21,Finformation becomes available."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
