OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,FMeanwhile Unite general secretary
OL,7,FSharon Graham has signalled concerns
OL,8,Fabout potential impact on the workforce
OL,10,F"Thankfully no-one was injured in the
OL,11,Ffire and workers were evacuated safely.
OL,13,F"However, the fire did cause
OL,14,Fsubstantial damage to a vital
OL,15,Fproduction line."
OL,17,FShe added: "Measures must now be put
OL,18,Fin place to protect jobs both at TATA
OL,19,Fand down the supply chain during any
OL,20,Fperiod of disruption.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@AOUwD@QO]yD@LOU
