OL,3,C'It was terrible': eyewitness
OL,4,Cdescribes the TATA Steel fire
OL,6,F"Meanwhile we are asking TATA and the
OL,7,FGovernment to ensure that operations
OL,8,Fare rebuilt as swiftly as possible."
